To install from a clean pull using 'make' (GNU make):

mkdir out
cd out
git submodule init
git submodule update
cmake -G "Unix Makefiles" ..
make libwiringPi libboost
make

To install from a clean pull using 'ninja' (Ninja):
mkdir out
cd out
git submodule init
git submodule update`
cmake -G "Ninja" ..
ninja libwiringPi
ninja libboost
ninja
